QuestData.Title: Bootlegger Outpost
QuestData.Description: We've done a bang up job here. I'm gonna make sure these mooks finish properly and then head back to Gadgetzan for a bit.$B$BIf you want to keep making a good impression on our Steamwheedle friends, or just make more money, you should head southwest of here. Bootlegger Outpost is set up on the edge of the gaping chasm.$B$BTalk to Zeke Bootscuff. I'd bet good money he'll need help.
QuestData.LogDescription: Talk to Zeke Bootscuff at Bootlegger Outpost.
QuestData.RewardText: You're with Megs, huh? Word is she's been pretty hell-bent on making nice with Noggenfogger.$B$BNot like I care. Are you ready to kill some bugs?
